name: Star mokka white dots
description:
Handmade star from India made from various high quality papers. Each piece is lavishly crafted and artfully designed. 
The paper stars shed a very cosy and soothing light. Perfect for Christmas decor or as an all year long decoration to create an atmospheric illumination of your home.

Height: 60 cm
Width: 60 cm
Depth: 20 cm
Diameter: 60 cm 

Each star comes folded with a manual on how to put them together effortlessly. Also included is a wall separator (if you want to use them as ceiling light) and a 3m plugging cable with a switch and socket E14.
